OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FBright
OL,6,For sunny spells and a chance of
OL,7,Fisolated, mainly light showers each
OL,8,Fday. Cooler midweek, with patchy
OL,9,Fovernight rural grass frost possible,
OL,10,Fturning milder again later. Winds
OL,11,Fgenerally light.
